               <note>
                  <date type="foundation" notBefore="1300" notAfter="1400">1300-1400</date>
                  
                  <ab type="history">Dabr. A new church is being built at the rock near the old rock-hewn church, with the burial of the local <persName ref="PRS12540SadeqanQahen">Ṣādǝqān</persName>. 
                     A recent church above on the plain is dedicated to <persName ref="PRS7049Michael" type="tabot">Michael</persName>.  &#xD;
</ab>
                  <ab type="description"><figure>
                     <graphic url="Sites/QES.tif">
                        <desc>The church photographed by Denis Nosnitsin during the Ethio-SPaRe project.</desc></graphic>
                  </figure>16 Mss. and 4 scroll photographed: <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes001">QES-001</ref> “Missal”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes002">QES-002</ref> “Vita of  George; Miracles of George”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes003">QES-003</ref> “Vita of the Righteous Ones”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes004">QES-004</ref> “Prayer of Incense and other texts”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes005">QES-005</ref> “Homiliary for the feasts St. Michael Miracles of St. Mikaʾel”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes006">QES-006</ref> “Vita of Righeous ones;               Miracles of the Righteous ones”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes007">QES-007</ref> “Vita of  ʾEwostatewos; Miracles of  ʾEwostatewos; Image of  ʾEwostatewos”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes008">QES-008</ref> “Book of the Marriage Ritual”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes009">QES-009</ref> “Book of the Covenant of the Righteous ones; Vita of the Righteous ones”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes010">QES-010</ref> “Bǝsratä Yoḥannǝs (fols. 3r-82r); Bǝsratä Marqos (<ref type="mss" corresp="ES83r122">83r-122</ref>vb); Fǝkare ʾIyäsus (1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES23ra132">23ra-132</ref>vb); Tǝnbitä Sabela (1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES33ra147">33ra-147</ref>); Dǝrsan Zä- Yohannǝs ʾAfäwärq (read on the feast of Rufaʾel ) (fols. 1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES41ra161">41ra-161</ref>rb); Täʾamrä Rufaʾel (1<ref type="mss" corresp="ES61rb192">61rb-192</ref>rb)”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes011">QES-011</ref> “Book of the Funeral Rite”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes012">QES-012</ref> “Bandlet of Righteousness”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes013">QES-013</ref> “Excerpts from Dǝqqwa”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes014">QES-014</ref> “Book of Hymns”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes015">QES-015</ref> “1Rite of the passion Week; Doctrina Arcanorum; Other texts for passion week ”; <ref type="mss" corresp="ESqes016">QES-016</ref> “Bandlet of Righteousness”.</ab>
  
                  <ab type="tabot">
                     <measure quantity="3"/>Tābots of <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh" type="tabot">Jesus</persName> and <persName ref="PRS6819Mary" type="tabot">Mary</persName> in the old church, 
                     <persName ref="PRS7049Michael" type="tabot">Michael</persName> in the upper church.</ab>
